    *   Execute as: **Me**.
    *   Who has access: **Only myself**.
    *   Click **Deploy**.
5.  **Authorize:** Google will ask for permission to read your Gmail. Click **Allow**.
6.  **Run:** Copy the **Web App URL** provided. Paste it into your browser.

**You are now live.** Click "SYNC NOW" and your Gmail alerts from the specified date will be analyzed and displayed in real-time.

